People are becoming more interested in studying in university. While some people think this is a bad development because students have more pressure, I believe it is a positive fact. This essay will explain why more people want to study in university and why I think so.

The main reason is that people want to learn more knowledge meanwhile get better jobs. This is becaus people holding a university degree have better roles in a variety of areas. As a result, people believe that going to university can help them have a better future. For example, many students study finance or AI because these jobs usually have higher salaries. This shows that university education can improve people's lives.

Another reason is that more university graduates can help society. If more people have good education, they can become doctors, teachers, scientists, or engineers. In other words, they can help solve problems and make the country better. For example, doctors can improve health care. Therefore, having more educated people is good for society.

Some people think that too many students go to university and not everyone can find a good job. This is not quite true. However, the government can build more universities or create more places to study to reduce the competition. Also, people stlll gain useful knowledge that can change their lifes even if they do not get their dream job.

In conclusion, although competition for university places is becoming harder I believe this is a positive situation because people can have better careers and society can become stronger.